title: Big Papi 5-CD Christmas Pack VIII (Jazz R&B Chipmunks Vocal)
description:
Big Papi has loads of Christmas music much of it not found anywhere else. Please search for "Big Papi Christmas" and please seed to keep the music alive. Don't be a Grinch that stole Christmas!! hee hee

For those who want to shuffle Christmas music as it plays, which is the only way to fly!, all you need to do is create a playlist and add all these albums to it. Once you have a playlist you can go inside of it and select shuffle. Now you have some good Christmas spirit going on that will impress all who listen to your choons.

- Big Papi
